channel.title: All my rsps stuff (Warning: if you are experienced, this is not good for you)
channel.description:
First of all, I would like to give credits and say some of this stuff is useless or on this forums Credits: Me 5% Everyone else 95%
This is basically all of the stuff I did on RSPS. I have my stuff from models to servers. And some of these are very old lol. This is good for noobs, anyone experienced will know this is shit. [b]I can post virus scans if you want me to.[/b]
Okay first off heres the modeling stuff. It has Gzip, Metasequioa, RIG by Frell, RSMV (doesn't work), DatMaker. The models that are there are: A bunch of custom items (like guns, weapons, recolored skillcapes), and a 481 model + item dump. http://up.ht/qwfga2
Secondly, here are some horrible projects I never got around to finish and because they got boring and stupid, One of them are All-Star Scape, Another is a Shard Server I don't want to do anymore, and the rest are deltascape. http://up.ht/qkQZsn
Well thats about it, hope someone has better fun than I did with them.
